{"tid":33434,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［歐聯］阿仙奴16強會唔會對皇馬？","createTime":"2016-12-10T19:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T07:10:19.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b04dbf10a455ff2fa6fd5be52bcdb5c448c874d","tid":33434,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T19:16:28.000Z","msg":"又16強出局？"},{"pid":"781596f92cb06ab6d989862a6859d1e01816b06e","tid":33434,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又16強出局？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n皇馬岀局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4796890fa3f67caabe5245b2c547fc9d61bc60e","tid":33434,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T20:28:14.000Z","msg":"個個都爭住同爺爺比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e65b95d1e9c1538c2292f704e1972859904db0e","tid":33434,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T00:36:23.000Z","msg":"16強出局就一定GE"},{"pid":"22a11e30951ca185414c0144cd35e11fb6a4402c","tid":33434,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T00:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又16強出局？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n皇馬岀局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/084108_8be87e281f5dd867e8cad2350180a9ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F084108_8be87e281f5dd867e8cad2350180a9ff.jpg&h=cdfc76c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c49a80110b4b7947047d8c62d09a495e1b101b5f","tid":33434,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"歐聯今抽籤槍手四面楚歌<br />\n<br />\n【綜合歐洲外電】歐洲足協在香港時間今晚舉行歐聯16強抽籤，很可能會抽出重頭大戰，因為皇家馬德里、拜仁慕尼黑及巴黎聖日耳門（PSG）等多支強隊都僅以次名晉級。（有線61及201台今日6:45pm直播）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n次名勁旅一籮<br />\n歐聯分組賽上周三完成，16支晉級球隊誕生。阿仙奴今屆爭氣，力壓PSG得到小組首名，外界關注兵工廠能否轉運，靠首名出線之利抽中實力較弱的次名球隊。然而，阿仙奴卻遇上近10屆歐聯最強的小組次名陣容，他們雖可以避開同國的曼城及同組的PSG，但有機會遇上上屆冠軍皇馬或上屆四強拜仁。阿仙奴還可能抽中鬥歐霸盃冠軍西維爾、葡超雙雄賓菲加、波圖，或者德甲的利華古遜。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n在歐聯16強抽籤後，歐洲足協隨即舉行歐霸盃32強抽籤（now670台今日8:00pm直播），在A組以次名出線的曼聯未能成為種籽隊，在下圈有機會遇上羅馬、史浩克04或費倫天拿等歐陸雄師。至於在歐聯分組賽得第三位的熱刺就被列為種籽，可能面對畢爾包、維拉利爾或慕遜加柏等。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/sports/art/20161212/19862940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsports%2Fart%2F20161212%2F19862940&d=axfG9w7FiuduG36e9geNTgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=0ac615a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsports%2Fart%2F20161212%2F19862940&h=e452157d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/sports/art/20161212/19862940</a>"},{"pid":"70e66271273e399282191a42b9a75eff60015a25","tid":33434,"uid":5386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"最強16郎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}